Package com.serezk4.command

package com.serezk4.command
Package for handling commands within the application.

Contains classes implementing various commands like add, remove, save, and execute script operations.

Since:
1.0

    Holds the active list of commands available in the application.

    Exit

    PrintFieldDescendingHairColor
    Command to print the hair color field of all persons in descending order.
    RemoveById
    Command to remove an element from the collection by its ID.
    RemoveFirst
    Command to remove the first element from the collection.
    RemoveGreater
    Command to remove all elements from the collection that are greater than the specified element.
    Save
    Command to save the current state of the collection to a file.
    Show
    Command to display all elements in the collection.
